ActFederal Public Sector Labour Relations Act
SubjectCanadian Food Inspection Agency-Public Service Alliance of Canada ** Collective Agreement **
PrecisOrder Approving that the ENTRY by the Canadian Food Inspection Agency into a COLLECTIVE AGREEMENT with the Public Service Alliance of Canada applicable to all employees of the Agency in the Public Service Alliance of Canada Bargaining Unit, which provides for the changes to the previous Collective Agreement and which expires on December 31, 2018.
